name: Data Read
func:
const data = msg.payload

if (data && Array.isArray(data)) {
    msg.CONV1 = msg.payload[0] //reverse 1000
    msg.CONV2 = msg.payload[1] //forward 1001
    msg.CONV4 = msg.payload[2] //Heater Coil 2 1002
    msg.CONV3 = msg.payload[3] // Heater Coil 1 1003
    msg.SC2 = msg.payload[4] //1004
    msg.SC1 = msg.payload[5] //1005
    msg.ExhaustFan = msg.payload[6] //1006
    msg.CoolingFan = msg.payload[7] //1007
    msg.Vibrator = msg.payload[8] //1008
    msg.topic = 'data'
    return msg;

} else return null

name: Write to modbus
Topic Setter
Response Message
func:
const button_name=msg.payload['address']
const value =msg.payload['value'][0]
const msgDict ={
    1000:"Dryer Forward",
    1001:"Dryer Reverse",
    1002:"Heater 1",
    1003:"Heater 2",
    1005:"SC1",
    1004:"SC2",
    1006:"Exhaust Fan",
    1007:"Cooling Fan",
    1008:"Vibrator",
}
const status = value===1?"turned ON":"turned OFF"
msg.payload={
    message:`${msgDict[button_name]} ${status} Successfully`
}
msg.topic='response'
return msg;
